262
0:15:33,059 --> 0:15:34,260
No lawyer?

263
0:15:34,260 --> 0:15:35,059
No witnesses?

264
0:15:35,619 --> 0:15:37,780
What sort of due process is this?

265
0:15:37,780 --> 0:15:40,979
Without actually establishing what these people are rebelling against,

266
0:15:40,979 --> 0:15:43,940
