268
0:15:47,780 --> 0:15:50,260
It's more of an issue of underdeveloped worldbuilding

269
0:15:50,260 --> 0:15:53,460
and not necessarily politically charged moralizing.

270
0:15:53,460 --> 0:15:57,219
As I said earlier, The Dark Knight Rises is far from a bad film.

271
0:15:57,219 --> 0:15:59,380
It unfortunately falls a bit short,

272
0:15:59,380 --> 0:16:01,859
but so goes the tragedy with many trilogies.

273
0:16:01,859 --> 0:16:05,700
With so many subplots, so many characters, so much ambition,

274
0:16:05,700 --> 0:16:07,380
and it being so long,

275
0:16:07,380 --> 0:16:10,099
